1. create a function that returns 'true' if a string is empty and 'false' other otherwise
2. create a method that takes any given number of string and concatenates them
3. write a function that returns the length of a string. Make your function recursive.
4. write a function that takes a string and returns it as an integer
5. create a function that returns true if a string contains whitespaces
6. create a funciton that adds a string to each member in an array
   overload to use StringBuilder
   measure elapsed time to perform task for both types
7. write a function that validates whether two strings are identical. Make it case insensitive.
8. create a function that takes two string and returns true if the first string ends with second string
9. create a function that returns "lower" if all letters are lowercase, returns "upper" if all letters are uppercase,
"mixed" for any mix of the two
10. create a function that takes an array and string and returns the index of string
11. create a function that takes a string and returns the number of words. The string will be a sentence.
12. create a function that takes a character and string and returns the number of times the character is found in the string
13. write a function that given a string returns the number of vowels contained within it
14. create a function that returns 'true' if a string contains only uppercase or only lowercase letters
15. create a function that takes a string and returns it in reverse order
16. create a function that takes a string and returns a string with space between characters
17. create a function that repeats each character 'n' times
18. create a function that takes a string of lowercase characters and returns that string reverse and capitalize
